do you like the music i'm playing?

do you like the music you're playing?

you didn't think it would be successful
i don't... i hadn't really thought it through. i didn't know that the band... was so important
i mean, what did you think i was gonna do?
i mean the long haul, like you're gonna stay in this band... for a long time... on tour

so it's like the long haul?
you know, we tour so we can make the record so we can go back and tour the record
but after we finish, we're gonna go to record and then we'll go back on tour
when are you finished with the whole tour?
what do you mean? i mean...
i know, but when are you done?
we're just gonna have to try and see each other, y'know, so that we see each other
so i don't really think that would be...
um... well all my stuff is here and it's in two weeks
yeah, but can't you rehearse anywhere?
what are you doing after the tour?
oh, that would be... really exciting. i wish i could
yeah, you can knock that off your bucketlist
